**Summary:** This documentation covers the Adjust attribution integration that uses Amplitude's Attribution API to send real-time user attribution data, requiring Advertising ID (IDFA/IDFV/ADID) matching and supporting user segmentation by ad parameters with a 72-hour attribution event retention window.

